    "shortName": {
      "zh": "TKPD",
      "en": "TKPD"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "TKPD (俄语“德拉贡诺夫重型支援卡宾枪”的缩写) 是 SVDK 狙击步枪的现代化升级版本，9.3x64 毫米口径，现已装备 BEAR PMC 行动人员进行测试。相比常规中口径狙击枪更加精确，在中远距离上对目标的压制效果更好。由 SniperArms Dynamics 公司设计制造。",
      "en": "The TKPD (Tyazhelyy Karabin Podderzhki Dragunova - \"Dragunov Heavy Support Carbine\") is a modernized SVDK chambered in 9.3x64mm, commissioned by PMC BEAR. The weapon is noted for high accuracy and effectively suppresses targets at medium ranges. Manufactured by SniperArms Dynamics."
    },
